column5: Lovely one story 2,300 sq. ft., 3 bedrooms 2 bath home on a large 1.25 acre lot perfect for Aggie GAME DAY or a quiet weekend. From the house Kyle Field is 5.5 miles. Easy access to highway 6. Convenient shopping centers and restaurants under a mile.
column8: Beautiful 3/2 home 5 miles from Texas A&M.
